    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Siphonolabrum tenebrosus n. sp. Non-ovigerous female. A, cheliped fixed finger detail; B, antennule, C, antenna (lateral view); D – E, labrum dorsal and lateral profile respectively; F, mandible; G, maxilla; H, maxillule endite, I, maxilliped palp, one omitted; J, maxilliped endite (distal); K, uropod. Scale bar = 0.25 mm for A-E, G, I-K, 0.125 mm for F and H." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/178700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

